#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:2
#: 17e3a931d3854933841762cf7cf15071
msgid "系统"
msgstr "System"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:17
#: fcff331839294be8a549e7c0e31f9976
msgid "CPU架构，运行频率以及RAM"
msgstr "CPU architecture, operating frequency, and RAM"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:18
#: 73add5d4dbe846a6a7b846b0b04c6bd0
msgid ""
"BL602是基于RISC-V处理器芯片，最高运行频率是160MHz,特殊情况下允许超频到192M，"
"芯片可用RAM。"
msgstr ""
"BL602 is based on a RISC-V processor chip. Its maximum operating frequency "
"is 160 MHz; in special cases, it can be overclocked to 192 MHz. The chip has "
"usable RAM."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:21
#: acb004a9599b468fa74cc2b259180f12
msgid "模组从上电到运行程序最快需要多长时间？"
msgstr ""
"What is the shortest time required for the module to run the program after "
"power-on?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:22
#: c3c2951df8364204aeade9d4dcf54603
msgid "约3ms。"
msgstr "About 3 ms."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:25
#: 6699af4390df4e19a28614d17304be31
msgid "模组掉电的时候，数据存储在哪里？"
msgstr "Where is data stored when the module is powered off?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:26
#: 3fea1912c10344388e53ffa8d2f8074e
msgid ""
"完全掉电时，芯片内ram上的数据均会丢失。PDS、HBN模式不同level下ram区域掉电情况"
"各不相同，需要case by case。"
msgstr ""
"When power is completely cut off, all data in the chip’s internal RAM will "
"be lost. In PDS and HBN modes, the RAM power-down status varies depending on "
"different levels and needs to be analyzed case by case."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:29
#: b3703db6edec4f4685924d3ba78b5be5
msgid "为什么模块默认支持Cli串口通讯，在哪设置不开启这个选型？"
msgstr ""
"Why does the module support CLI serial communication by default, and where "
"can this option be disabled?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:30
#: 10e8e29e28764ddabd94dd4bcfd7b697
msgid ""
"我们移植了命令行交互工具cli（command-line interface），已经将其移植到我们到系"
"统中，在对应的工程目录的 proj_config.mk 文件把 CONFIG_SYS_AOS_CLI_ENABLE:=0，"
"如果没有，则添加这个设置。"
msgstr ""
"We have ported the command-line interaction tool CLI (command-line "
"interface) into the system. To disable it, set the following in the "
"proj_config.mk file under the corresponding project directory: "
"CONFIG_SYS_AOS_CLI_ENABLE:=0. If this setting does not exist, add it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:33
#: ffc82cd960194de08fca203047f73ef9
msgid "为什么我写的组件或代码，无法开启LOG打印日志？"
msgstr "Why can't the component or code I wrote enable LOG printing?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:34
#: 3b046309a75f4da68f75bf26bef340f5
msgid ""
"日志管理组件blog开关需在相应的 proj_config.mk 文件目录下，"
"LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS配置上增加对应组件的名字 例如这里需要增加blog_testa "
"blog_testb blog_testc 的日志输出：LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS:=blog_testa "
"blog_testb blog_testc 其他组件默认关闭，组件名字就是其文件夹名字。"
msgstr ""
"The switch for the log management component blog must be configured in the "
"corresponding proj_config.mk file directory. Add the corresponding component "
"names to LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS. For example, to enable log output for "
"blog_testa, blog_testb, and blog_testc, configure: LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS:"
"=blog_testa blog_testb blog_testc. Other components are disabled by default. "
"The component name is the same as its folder name."
